        "product_page_accordion_wDmbQ9": {
          "type": "productPageAccordion",
          "settings": {
            "noMargin": false,
            "accCustomID": "",
            "heading": "Delivery information",
            "content": "custom",
            "metafieldNS": "global",
            "metafieldKey": "",
            "page": "",
            "customContent": "<p>Experience swift and seamless service with our *free 5-10 day delivery to UK addresses! Our dedicated 2-person team ensures your new mattress is delivered right to your room of choice. </p><p>Please note that some further reaching postcodes in Scotland, Northern Ireland and islands are on longer lead times - input your address at the checkout for information on your area. </p>\n\n<p>Express next working day delivery is available on the Pocket 1000 mattress in single, double &amp; UK king size. This delivery service is to the front door of the property only for this service. </p>\n\n<p>Enhance your convenience further by opting for old mattress removal at checkout for a nominal fee.\n </p>\n\n\n<p>Enjoy complete flexibility with delivery dates: Our courier will contact you via email and WhatsApp, providing a selection of dates to choose from. The day before delivery, you'll receive an advisory 3-hour time window. The drivers will call when they're just 30 minutes away - Your comfort is our priority!</p>"
          }
        },
        "product_page_accordion_Eg6NWd": {
          "type": "productPageAccordion",
          "settings": {
            "noMargin": true,
            "accCustomID": "",
            "heading": "Old mattress collection",
            "content": "custom",
            "metafieldNS": "global",
            "metafieldKey": "",
            "page": "",
            "customContent": "<p>We can collect and recycle your old mattress when we deliver your new one. A small recycling fee applies, which will be clearly shown during checkout. </p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_group_end_delivery": {
