    "ss_testimonial_8_wyrAAU": {
      "type": "ss-testimonial-8",
      "blocks": {
        "slide_6c4pcc": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "600 & 500 (5 year review)",
            "text": "Easy to order, keep their word on trial period (there was one mattress that was not suitable and had to be returned), and I have tried multiple hybrid mattresses and this is by far the best at a reasonable cost. We have 4 mattress from REM-fit and intending to get more. We have both the Ortho 500 (x2) and Remfit 600 (x2) haven’t looked back! My back pain better, I sleep cooler and more comfortably. Seeing my satisfaction my family has been following suit one by one. The quality is excellent and the team accessible. Ps the review is for the latest one that I bought for my nephew but I have had mine for last 5 years",
            "author_date": "Bill Hughes"
          }
        },
        "slide_WXTJg4": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Heaven (600 Lux Elite)",
            "text": "So, I ordered the wrong size mattress and they sorted it before delivery and were fantastic. The delivery was smooth and the delivery guys were absolutely lovely.The mattress itself is just amazing. I am a terrible insomniac and this mattress (i ordered the medium firmness) has genuinely improved the amount of sleep I get and most definitely the quality of that sleep. £600 seems like a lot of money but it is absolutely money well spent as sleep is so important. Absolutely fantastic purchase!",
            "author_date": "Kirsty Bob"
          }
        },
        "slide_b8VqEG": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Ortho 500 mattress did wonders for my herniated discs",
            "text": "I bought the ortho 500 mattress after suffering several chronic herniated discs. I have not had a crisis since using this mattress. 10/10 would recommend to anyone",
            "author_date": "Charlotte"
          }
        },
        "slide_AA6xty": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "400 mattress and 500 cool gel pillows",
            "text": "We now own a rem-fit 400 hybrid mattress for over 2 weeks and rem-fit 500 cool gel pillows for over 4 years, and I cannot recommend their products enough.They’re comfortable and comforting, the mattress feels like a supportive cloud and the pillows have stopped me having constant neck pains.",
            "author_date": "Chris"
          }
        },
        "slide_W6d8ip": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Mattress has not disappointed (600 Lux)",
            "text": "I chose this mattress as it was recommended by Which? for the features that were important and it has not disappointed. The ordering process and delivery arrangements were straightforward, but most of all the mattress has provided the support and comfort needed and is certainly an improvement on the old well-worn mattress I was using.",
            "author_date": "Mr. Ewens"
          }
        },
        "slide_GwaEDn": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "This is possibly the best customer service",
            "text": "This is possibly the best customer service I have received in years. From start to finish the experience was great. Real people, fast answers to questions, multiple solution options. This is how customer care was and should be.",
            "author_date": "Neil Mcnamee"
          }
        },
        "slide_mN7xrU": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "400 Elite Mattress",
            "text": "I've been sleeping on the 400 Elite mattress for over 6 months now and can only sing its praises. For me, pressure point relief is a must as I predominantly sleep on my side - this mattress performs perfectly for me and still feels supportive despite it's soft sleeping surface. I've now just treated myself to one of their 500 pillows.",
            "author_date": "RH"
          }
        },
        "slide_BxDFHW": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Fantastic purchase (600 Lux)",
            "text": "Fantastic purchase, so comfy after months of waking up with back and shoulder pain. Totally recommend rem-fit 600 . After reviewing mattresses for a good few weeks I'm so glad went with these opposed the the other 3 big names",
            "author_date": "Julie Beerling"
          }
        },
        "slide_c49BWU": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "I had issues with back pain (500 Ortho Elite)",
            "text": "I had issues with back pain, especially after a night's sleep. I ve tried Ergoflex and Simba but I would always wake up with back pain. Using recently a firm REM-Fit mattress I woke up with a lot less back pain",
            "author_date": "Costas Tsakonas"
          }
        },
        "slide_PH8x78": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Best Pillow (500 Cool Gel)",
            "text": "This is the best pillow I have ever had. It is the perfect height and super comfortable, offering excellent neck support for both sleeping and reading in bed.The pillow arrived quickly and well packaged. Highly recommend.",
            "author_date": "Nicola"
          }
        },
        "slide_TiQG6M": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Love Love Love! (600 Lux Elite)",
            "text": "Love Love Love!! The delivery guys didn’t moran they had to carry my mattress up 2 flights of stairs! They were jolly and friendly and the mattress is brilliant!! Just as good as my friends Tempur but much more reasonably priced!! I am VERY HAPPY! Thank you!! Happy New Ye….. MATTRESS!! 😘😘",
            "author_date": "Patricia Ferry"
          }
        },
        "slide_wPeBBq": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Extremely comfortable (Pocket 1000)",
            "text": "Extremely comfortable mattress and no more aches and pains! Great customer service 👏 👌",
            "author_date": "S. Bass"
          }
        },
        "slide_nPKkWE": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 4,
            "heading": "Good supported pillows",
            "text": "Bought 2 pillows, one for me (400 Memory Foam) and one for husband (500 Cool Gel) and have been happy with our purchase. I have noticed my neck is supported better and less headaches in the morning. Got the discount for buying 2 and the Over 50's which helped with the price.",
            "author_date": "Johanna Hardy"
          }
        },
        "slide_aLYaek": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 4,
            "heading": "Cozy (500 Ortho)",
            "text": "This is the second mattress we have purchased from rem fit we had bought our first mattress 5 years ago for our bed so when we decided to replace the mattress on the spare room bed we had no hesitation in buying from rem fit. Good value for money.",
            "author_date": "Anonymous"
          }
        },
        "slide_9E7m3C": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Thanks for the great customer service",
            "text": "Bought a mattress from Rem-fit and it arrived on time. After sleeping for a few nights we realized that it was too soft for us and that we prefer something firmer. Rem-fit have processed our return request under the 100 night sleep trial. Thanks for the great customer service",
            "author_date": "Hashan Dias"
          }
        },
        "slide_a7GWCJ": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "REM-Fit 400 Hybrid Mattress",
            "text": "REM-Fit 400 Hybrid Mattress. Our bed is electrical adjustable so a single mattress was not an option. Recently I came across REM online and after a little thought decided to buy one for myself and was delighted with the result. The mattress in neither hard nor soft, but is firm and extremely comfortable. I liked the experience so much I bought one for my wife also and she now is able to to get a full undisturbed nights sleep also",
            "author_date": "Bill Hughes"
          }
        },
        "slide_gDg3g7": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "The quality is excellent (Pocket 1000)",
            "text": "The quality is excellent for the affordable price. I purchased the Rem-Fit 1000 mattress, and it meets our expectations. It's more medium than medium-firm, but that's exactly what we needed. Although delivery was delayed, they arranged for it to arrive the next day.",
            "author_date": "Jas Berd"
          }
        },
        "slide_DfCfUe": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Highly Recommended company (500 Ortho)",
            "text": "Second mattress from this company, have a king we bought several years back which is still going strong (ortho 500) and just bought a double of the same for another room. Mattresses are absolutely spot on really comfy and fantastic quality, customer support is also excellent.",
            "author_date": "Sarah Hird"
          }
        },
        "slide_fa9TaD": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Sweet dreams! I hope! (500 Ortho)",
            "text": "A lot of reading reviews and with so many companies now saying how great they are the reviews are important.Delivery was as stated and very polite service.It’s early days but I will take advantage of the sleep trial which gives me peace of mind when spending so much money.The website picked the correct mattress based on how I sleep.",
            "author_date": "Wendy Allen"
          }
        },
        "slide_NAw8VK": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "REM-Fit 600 Lux Elite Hybrid Mattress",
            "text": "Very happy with the REM-Fit 600® Lux Elite Hybrid Mattress and service from start to finish. Mattress was delivered directly to the room and the old mattress removed without fuss. It took a few days to get used to the firmness however that probably had more to do with the old mattress which was approx 10 years old.",
            "author_date": "Peter Teesdale"
          }
        },
        "slide_XyNYnP": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "I ordered the REM 600 Lux Hybrid…",
            "text": "I ordered the REM 600 Lux Hybrid mattress. Order and delivery spot on. I can say at 58 I’ve found the perfect mattress for me…. I’m can’t rate it enough.",
            "author_date": "Barbara Ellwood"
          }
        },
        "slide_wg7Lgn": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "600 Lux mattress",
            "text": "Easy to order, quick delivery with timed delivery slot. Used for a week now and Oh my goodness a magic nights sleep, big financial outlay but worth every penny paid.",
            "author_date": "Gdmacduff18"
          }
        },
        "slide_e8q8Ma": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "Back pain gone (600 Lux)",
            "text": "We’ve had our 600 lux mattress for four weeks now and it’s blissfully comfortable. We had a memory foam mattress before and spent a lot of money on it.I was experiencing problems with my thoracic spine and would be shifting around all through the night to alleviate pain.From the first night the difference was really noticeable and now after four weeks I have no issues at all. Going to bed is a joy. Wish I’d bought it sooner.",
            "author_date": "Jane Willcocks"
          }
        },
        "slide_87rgFR": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "stars_count": 5,
            "heading": "REM-Fit 400 Hybrid Mattress",
            "text": "REM-Fit 400 Hybrid Mattress. Our bed is electrical adjustable so a single mattress was not an option. Recently I came across REM online and after a little thought decided to buy one for myself and was delighted with the result. The mattress in neither hard nor soft, but is firm and extremely comfortable. I liked the experience so much I bought one for my wife also and she now is able to to get a full undisturbed nights sleep also",
            "author_date": "Bill Hughes"
          }
        }
      },
